snippet: Wimbledon champion Andy Murray says "it's looking unlikely" that he will play for Britain in its Davis Cup quarterfinal against Serbia this week....
lead_paragraph: Wimbledon champion Andy Murray says "it's looking unlikely" that he will play for Britain in its Davis Cup quarterfinal against Serbia this week.
